high_descs: Go forward to the side table, hang a left and go to the couch where the computer is.
Pick up the keys that are left of the computer from the couch.
Turn to the left and go to the end of the table, turn to the left, go forward, turn to the left, go to the shelf with the TV on it that is on the right.
Put the keys on the bottom right shelf under the TV.
Hang a left and go to the chair, turn to the left, go to the second chair on the right.
Pick up the keys that are in the chair.
Turn to the right, go forward, hang a right and go to the shelf with the TV on it that is on the left.
Put the keys on the bottom right shelf under the TV with the other keys.
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of keys on a shelf.

high_descs: Move to and face the center of the black couch in front of the picture frame on the wall.
Pick up the set of keys between the red credit card and the laptop from the couch.
Move around past the coffee table and move to the black entertainment center in front of the television.
Place the set of keys on the bottom right shelf of the entertainment center.
Turn left, move around the coffee table to the chair to the right of the potted plant.
Pick up the set of keys from the chair.
Turn right, move around the coffee table and move to the entertainment center in front of the television.
Place the set of keys on top of the set of keys on the bottom right shelf of the entertainment center.
anns.task_desc: Place two sets of keys in the entertainment center.

high_descs: Walk forward to the couch then step to your left.
Pick up the keys that are to the left of the laptop.
Walk over to the tv that's to your left and stand in front of it facing it.
Put the keys on the bottom right shelf.
Turn left and walk to the black chair then move left to face the chair to the left of the first one.
Pick up the set of keys on the cushion.
Walk back to where you put the first set of keys.
Put these keys near where you put the first set.
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of keys on the shelf.
